name: UIDataDetectorTypes
desc: Constants that define the types of information to detect in text-based content.

items.name: static var phoneNumber: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect strings with the format of a phone number.

items.name: static var link: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect strings with the format of a URL.

items.name: static var address: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect strings with the format of an address.

items.name: static var calendarEvent: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect strings with the format of a calendar event.

items.name: static var shipmentTrackingNumber: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect strings with the format of a tracking number from a package delivery company.

items.name: static var flightNumber: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect strings with the format of a flight number from an airline.

items.name: static var lookupSuggestion: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect strings with the format of information that the user might want to look up.

items.name: static var all: UIDataDetectorTypes
items.desc: An option to detect all available types of data.

items.name: init(rawValue: UInt)
items.desc: Creates a data detector type with the specified raw value.
